12 rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8\"><p class=\"max-w-4xl text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85 md:text-lg\">A single corporate master page — story, leadership, investment profile, governance, and reference — aligned to company-context.md.</p></div><div class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/90 md:text-[17px] md:leading-8 [&amp;_strong]:font-semibold [&amp;_strong]:text-brand-blue\"><section class=\"bg-slate-50 py-28 first:pt-10\"><div class=\"grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center lg:gap-20\"><div class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/60 bg-white shadow-2xl shadow-brand-blue/5\"><img alt=\"Hydropower site placeholder — engineering and construction\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 40vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1581092160607-ee22621dd758%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/5] w-full\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 to-transparent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-stretch gap-4\"><span class=\"w-[2px] shrink-0 bg-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div class=\"w-full\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-cyan\">Our story</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 max-w-none font-heading text-3xl font-bold leading-[1.2] tracking-tight text-brand-blue md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl\">A Decade of<!-- --> <span class=\"whitespace-nowrap\">Engineering Excellence</span>.</h2></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-6 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/90 md:text-[17px] md:leading-8\"><p><strong>Unitech Hydropower Company Limited</strong> was first registered as a <strong>Private Limited</strong> company under the Companies Act of Nepal and later converted to a<!-- --> <strong>Public Limited</strong> company to support growth, transparency, and broader stakeholder participation.</p><p>The conversion registration is recorded as<!-- --> <strong>BS 2079/10/06</strong> (no.<!-- --> <strong>306353/079/080</strong>). The original private registration is <strong>BS 2071/06/10</strong> (no.<!-- --> <strong>127161/071/072</strong>).</p><p>We develop run-of-river hydropower with modern technology, environmental responsibility, and transparent delivery.</p><p><a class=\"font-semibold text-brand-blue underline-offset-4 hover:underline\" href=\"/projects\">View projects</a><span class=\"text-brand-slate/50\"> · </span><a class=\"font-semibold text-brand-blue underline-offset-4 hover:underline\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></p></div><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><div class=\"w-fit rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white px-4 py-3 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-4 w-4 text-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Est.</p></div><p class=\"mt-2 font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-blue\">2014</p></div><div class=\"w-fit rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white px-4 py-3 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-landmark h-4 w-4 text-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M11.12 2.198a2 2 0 0 1 1.76.006l7.866 3.847c.476.233.31.949-.22.949H3.474c-.53 0-.695-.716-.22-.949z\"></path><path d=\"M14 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M18 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M3 22h18\"></path><path d=\"M6 18v-7\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Public Ltd</p></div><p class=\"mt-2 font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-blue\">2023</p></div><div class=\"w-fit rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white px-4 py-3 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Project location</p></div><div class=\"mt-2 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin h-4 w-4 text-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><p class=\"font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-blue\">Taplejung &amp; Panchthar, Nepal</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-slate-200/60 bg-slate-50 py-28\"><div class=\"grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center lg:gap-20\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-8 w-[2px] shrink-0 bg-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-cyan\">The vision</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 max-w-[22ch] text-balance font-heading text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.2] tracking-tight text-brand-blue lg:text-5xl\">Leadership for Nepal’s energy future.</h2></div></div><p class=\"mt-8 font-heading text-2xl font-bold leading-snug tracking-tight text-brand-blue md:text-3xl\">“It gives me great pleasure to welcome you to Unitech Hydropower Company Limited.”</p><div class=\"mt-8 max-w-2xl space-y-6 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/90 md:text-[17px] md:leading-8\"><p>Since our establishment, we have remained committed to contributing to Nepal&#x27;s growing energy needs through the sustainable development of hydropower resources.</p><p>Our transition from private to public limited status reflects a commitment to <strong>growth, transparency</strong>, and broader stakeholder participation — guided by <strong>integrity</strong>,<strong> accountability</strong>, and <strong>innovation</strong>.</p><p class=\"text-xs leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/60\">Condensed from themes recorded in<!-- --> <span class=\"font-medium text-brand-slate\">company-context.md</span>.</p></div></div><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/60 bg-white shadow-2xl shadow-brand-blue/5 lg:col-span-5 lg:min-h-[560px]\"><img alt=\"Professional portrait placeholder — Anoj Khadka\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 40vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1524504388940-b1c1722653e1%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1524504388940-b1c1722653e1%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1524504388940-b1c1722653e1%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1524504388940-b1c1722653e1%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1524504388940-b1c1722653e1%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2